span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://libguides.marquette.edu/content.php?pid=197124&amp;sid=1651941\">http://libguides.marquette.edu/content.php?pid=197124&amp;sid=1651941</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://careers.uw.edu/ifiles/all/files/docs/gradstudents/pdfs/AcademicCareers-Research_Statements_07-08.pdf\">http://careers.uw.edu/ifiles/all/files/docs/gradstudents/pdfs/AcademicCareers-Research_Statements_07-08.pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.upei.ca/~xliu/ed611/day3.htm\">http://www.upei.ca/~xliu/ed611/day3.htm</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.sbcc.edu/clrc/files/wl/downloads/DevelopingaThesisStatement.pdf\">http://www.sbcc.edu/clrc/files/wl/downloads/DevelopingaThesisStatement.pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://grantscourse.columbia.edu/CUMC-JSR_Funding_for_Graduate_Students_Research_Statement.pdf\">http://grantscourse.columbia.edu/CUMC-JSR_Funding_for_Graduate_Students_Research_Statement.pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Research_statement&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span clas